{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Something didn't-- didn't click right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And there were rumors they were demantling machinery already in the factory before, and they were shipping it back into Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But of course, we-- you have no contact with the outside world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "You don't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "The war, invade-- we didn't know any of those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And occasionally, we had seen a Russian plane flying, but that wasn't anything to, you know, make a roof over their cell, but the things started when they gradually exchanged the SS guards.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "More of the younger people, more of the younger guards, were replaced with older guards, men in their 60s or 50s, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And the bad thing, of course, was that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, looking back, you think, OK, you take a young German who grew up in the Hitler Jugend who was trained, and educated, and-- and taught all the Nazi theories.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "He probably might not have known better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But to take a man who is in his 60s and who has a family and to do the same thing that this young person did-- he did, and they'd try to keep up and make sure that they did just as good a job with-- than the younger ones did, and they did.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I sometimes wonder, looking back-- I wish I would have met somebody who would have shown a little compassion, understanding, would have given an extra piece of bread or something like that so at least at this time I could say, well, they weren't all bad.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Didn't occur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I wish sometime it would.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
